{"tid":1771360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"愛華頓炒馬高施華 鄧肯費格遜暫代","createTime":"2019-12-05T23:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T14:30:36.000Z","uid":36238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ca31164a6dbdd20f720753f14e71708bf8e623fe","tid":1771360,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T23:05:48.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】愛華頓於周四宣佈辭退馬高施華，暫由名將鄧肯費格遜領軍。<br />\n<br />\n馬高施華（Marco Silva）於周四與球會班主會面後，落實失去飯碗，會方所發表的聲明指，感謝施華過去18個月來的努力，祝他未來事事順利，而球隊暫時由昔日長人中鋒鄧肯費遜以看守領隊領軍，周六率兵出鬥車路士。 <br />\n<br />\n42歲的葡萄牙主帥施華於2018年5月才上任，領軍18個月期間戰績為60場24勝12和24負。自從馬天尼斯於2016年5月離任後，拖肥先後由朗奴高文、艾拿戴斯及馬高施華領軍都未能取得成功。 <br />\n<br />\n拖肥於周三以2:5被同市死敵利物浦所敗後，慘遭3連敗，聯賽排名跌至倒數第3位，成為施華的催命符。消息指，鄧肯費格遜只是暫代性質，前領隊莫耶斯是其中一個繼任可能人選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=27756382565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D27756382565&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=2c7ec25e\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=27756382565</a>"},{"pid":"a3110592e29c17039fb646e25cfac909c60e9299","tid":1771360,"uid":75028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T23:10:32.000Z","msg":"又係00年代既明叔教返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ecc539ea7ce88a80e2bc16b08eea55c7b62f09","tid":1771360,"uid":19552,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T23:39:55.000Z","msg":"又係高普"},{"pid":"db53d6889c2f6816776604d34bb06ec2659ba8f7","tid":1771360,"uid":8968,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"54ecc539ea7ce88a80e2bc16b08eea55c7b62f09","tid":1771360,"uid":19552,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T23:39:55.000Z","msg":"又係高普"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T23:49:24.000Z","msg":"班主都幾忍得馬高施華"},{"pid":"1f8de0e9c6702ab8f51e75bdc6167b3e25f79e6d","tid":1771360,"u